    "body": "**Problem**: Computing number of threads for parallel asynchronous computation using `uv.cpu_info()` can be slow. This is especially noticeable since it is pre-computed on every `require('vim.pack')` and not only when parallelism is needed.\r\n\r\n**Solution**: Use `uv.available_parallelism()` to compute number of threads in a helper function.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nFix #38644.",
    "closed_at": "2026-04-05T17:06:01Z",
    "comment_data": [
        {
            "_links": {
                "html": {
